I2C devices, that shall be powered down when non-interactive, are defined according to InputDevicePowerMonitorInfo.h. Name the source file to InputDevicePowerMonitorInfo.cpp and put it in vendor/intel/hardware/libpower/i2c/$(TARGET_PRODUCT) directory. E.g Harris Beach implementation of i2c devices definition is located in vendor/intel/hardware/libpower/i2c/hsb
